  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Mega Corporation Mining Industry!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Welcome to your new job as a <strong>Space Operator at Mega Corporation Mining Industry</strong>. We expect nothing but excellence from you given your application. <strong>Do not disappoint us</strong>\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up from your long sleep in the hyperchamber. But how did you actually pass the interview? Anyway, you must prove your skills now to make your parents proud. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/4569ce1b5e253e6b84d08b510a1fdca5.poster.avif?t=1747312139\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/4569ce1b5e253e6b84d08b510a1fdca5.webm?t=1747312139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/4569ce1b5e253e6b84d08b510a1fdca5.mp4?t=1747312139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control your drone!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where resources are slim, you have to operate drones to win against other mega-companies in battles on various moons in order to harvest the resources from the moons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the calm yet exciting atmosphere of this retro 2D turn-based pixel game and capture the moons for the Mega Corporation Mining Industry. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/72f5d0254473a755beee230fdf6318b0.poster.avif?t=1747312139\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/72f5d0254473a755beee230fdf6318b0.webm?t=1747312139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/72f5d0254473a755beee230fdf6318b0.mp4?t=1747312139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>These are the currently available features. We aim to add more throughout Early Access.</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19 unique missions across various moons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 endless minigames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 different weapons of choice</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Try out the free demo and wishlist Space Operators now!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/f043f2db8d43ac5197b741106049838c.avif?t=1747312139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras_big/f043f2db8d43ac5197b741106049838c.avif?t=1747312139 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Mega Corporation Mining Industry!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Welcome to your new job as a <strong>Space Operator at Mega Corporation Mining Industry</strong>. We expect nothing but excellence from you given your application. <strong>Do not disappoint us</strong>\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up from your long sleep in the hyperchamber. But how did you actually pass the interview? Anyway, you must prove your skills now to make your parents proud. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/4569ce1b5e253e6b84d08b510a1fdca5.poster.avif?t=1747312139\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/4569ce1b5e253e6b84d08b510a1fdca5.webm?t=1747312139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/4569ce1b5e253e6b84d08b510a1fdca5.mp4?t=1747312139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control your drone!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where resources are slim, you have to operate drones to win against other mega-companies in battles on various moons in order to harvest the resources from the moons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the calm yet exciting atmosphere of this retro 2D turn-based pixel game and capture the moons for the Mega Corporation Mining Industry. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/72f5d0254473a755beee230fdf6318b0.poster.avif?t=1747312139\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/72f5d0254473a755beee230fdf6318b0.webm?t=1747312139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/72f5d0254473a755beee230fdf6318b0.mp4?t=1747312139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>These are the currently available features. We aim to add more throughout Early Access.</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19 unique missions across various moons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 endless minigames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 different weapons of choice</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Try out the free demo and wishlist Space Operators now!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/f043f2db8d43ac5197b741106049838c.avif?t=1747312139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras_big/f043f2db8d43ac5197b741106049838c.avif?t=1747312139 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
